Package Cafe

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Customizable
    Java Interface implemented by some classes of Cafe package
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Coffee
    Coffee class creates instances of menuItems that are specific to Coffee Coffee is customizable with add-ins and have different sizes/prices
    CurrentOrderController
    CurrentOrderController is the operational class for the JavaFX CurrentOrder GUI
    Donut
    Donut Class represents instances of menuItem that are specific to donuts Each donut has a type, price, flavour, and quantity
    Main  
    MainMenuController
    MainMenuController is the operational class for the JavaFX StoreOrder GUI
    MenuItem
    MenuItem class is the superclass for the subclasses Donut and Coffee Stored in Order class array.
    Order
    Order class representing a list of all MenuItem objects
    OrderingCoffeeController
    OrderingCoffeeController is the operational class for the JavaFX OrderingCoffee GUI
    OrderingDonutController
    OrderingDonutController is the operational class for the JavaFX OrderingDonuts GUI
    StoreOrderController
    StoreOrderController is the operational class for the JavaFX StoreOrder GUI
    StoreOrders
    StoreOrder representing a list of all Order objects
